#define  rac mix(.5,3.,sin(iTime)*.5+.5)
//.5== circle;  5.= pretty straight red segment;  +inf=straight red segment.
/*
the 3rd/larger circle contains the 2 smaller circles and touches them at 1 point.
This results in a very precise egg-shaped distance field:

A rounder "tangential capsule" has the middle part not as straight line, 
but a 3rd large circle with a radius 
