//
// More Distance  by Timo Kinnunen 2017
//
// Comparison of two alternative distance functions
// and the builtin function over the whole 32bit
// floating point range, around 2^-128 to 2^+128.
//
// Use mouse to move the target point around.
//
// Default function is in red. On my computer it
// only produces usable results for about half of
// the available value range. Disappointing.
//
// The current and future exponents is plotted in black.
// White color indicates large or infinite values.
// Fully saturated R,G,B colors indicate zeros.
